# ── Admin env (Vite SPA) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy to .env.local. Vite only exposes VITE_*-prefixed vars to the client bundle.
# CRITICAL: only the ANON key goes here. The service-role key must NEVER be in the
# admin bundle — admins authenticate with their own JWT and RLS authorizes them.

